{"tid":2245504,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"諾翹 Lockill FACEOFF 口罩 好唔好用?","createTime":"2020-10-16T09:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T09:26:06.000Z","uid":380027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2993eeed77029ccf71c4945eaa59568f2aed7db1","tid":2245504,"uid":380027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:26:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 之前一直有使用可再用嘅Banale MASK, 定期換濾芯, 其實效果都幾好, 有次屋企搞小工程, 口罩都隔到化學物質味, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5mdwGJJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5mdwGJJ.png&h=3d43775d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但帶咗一段時間, 發現單手除唔方便, 之餘果咀又唔舒服,同埋自己大汗, 條繩都開始變色, 同埋行出街都幾誇張...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然一次性口罩價位明顯回落, 但始終感覺唔太環保. 我又開始搜羅可重用口罩, 響網絡上無意發現以下口罩, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3reEuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3reEuZ.jpg&h=6d0dfedc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢聲稱高透氣, 舒適等等, 其後發現佢有幾款限定版, 響不同黃色平台售賣, 估計係黃色口罩廠, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wxhp1Jk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxhp1Jk.jpg&h=66ffee1b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n請有冇巴絲用過? 耳仔位長帶12小時會唔會唔舒服? 有冇其他介紹? 謝謝"}]}